Ace singer, Tiwa Savage has offered insights on what happens to an individual who decides to engage in an argument with a fool. The 42-year-old “Somebody’s Son” singer in an Instagram post shared photos and video adorned in outfit she rocked to perform at Rick Ross’ Easter concert.   TikTok impact on music, distribution in Nigeria     Agbani Horsefall speaks on new gospel karaoke studio     Music Business Academy for Africa bounces back   While captioning her post, ‘Africa’s number one bad gyal’ stated a person automatically becomes a fool when they decide to argue with one. “When you argue with a fool, it only proves there are two,” Savage wrote.